{"tid":205994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好似被罰款？","createTime":"2017-04-18T07:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T13:27:13.000Z","uid":5429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b535d45d9f23d92bfc2f234bb103f14b7f4c7c7","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的 上個月我女友手機合約到期就轉咗台<br />\n點知依家過咗成個月 send咗條信息話要交三千幾蚊 話續咗約 毀約依家要罰款<br />\n之後明明個合約期係三月 （因為轉台前有上網睇過自己account合約期）依家佢就吹到係六月 但個account又上唔返去  <br />\n個number係佢老母嘅 老母都冇話續約過<br />\n但轉台前幾日我女友好似聽過一個電話 就係舊電訊商打嘅 佢又唔知點解講咗佢媽媽嘅個人資料 唔知係續約 <br />\n依家打返去舊電信商度 佢就話要交毀約罰款 我話要佢俾段續約嘅錄音我 佢就話要搵搵 <br />\n其實依家應該點？ 有冇彎轉？一定要交錢？唔知電訊商有冇續約錄音？但續約嘅都唔係佢吖媽本人，其實有冇效？我女友果時好亂，先講咗佢吖媽啲個人資料，以為係cut約嘅。<br />\nsorry for1999"},{"pid":"aa2615f2bd77d44d946a875e88b1368640b4cc69","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d40c5c5c70a215936ac092ec76e09b78829687","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:21:17.000Z","msg":"利申：依家用緊新電訊商 所以唔知點算"},{"pid":"9c2ff44d8f3eade17e2735791cdf325e3ce144ed","tid":205994,"uid":101322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"唔識 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542406737d9a8fed94535a5cff51068fa9028f39","tid":205994,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"on9女友<br />\n飛撚左佢"},{"pid":"1710da10e719ce28a0333dfcb68f60138d98b8f4","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9女友<br />\n飛撚左佢</blockquote><br />\n姐係要俾硬？"},{"pid":"e4eaff778aae0ba93798e86def97a89390d47add","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:33:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f15a2fd78b3daf5a8b604c02ade2ba1c167605","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"唔好沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de0ffef7f35f1c3202aec2ba3b795f0ed8b6b58","tid":205994,"uid":42850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:39:26.000Z","msg":"唔知咩事都可以比媽媽個人資料人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdbfc427cea916ee36a221ddf446bd04432774d","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知咩事都可以比媽媽個人資料人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係因為用我個名轉台 有人打嚟話續約佢以為係<br />\n 不過講佢吖媽啲個人資料又真係.....佢話當時懵咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e182e97cfa3ff0c8777b02f1b8e7152e274ea391","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfb9c38b3ec06410596f44022539944f5a08e4e","tid":205994,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"平時打去開通d咩服務都要對下資料係咪本人啦。<br />\n叫佢呀媽告個女盜用身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁應該唔洗罰款。"},{"pid":"6d91692ffd7d55b14cfe7b1a92004f157507799c","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時打去開通d咩服務都要對下資料係咪本人啦。<br />\n叫佢呀媽告個女盜用身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁應該唔洗罰款。</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以話以為係cut合約？ 幾個鐘錢打俾佢佢有話有錄音 話同事會覆返嚟 依家電話都未響過"},{"pid":"c9c07bf838944addbded757c5bf859420728d793","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時打去開通d咩服務都要對下資料係咪本人啦。<br />\n叫佢呀媽告個女盜用身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁應該唔洗罰款。</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以話以為係cut合約？ 幾個鐘<span style=\"color: red;\">錢</span>打俾佢 佢有話有錄音 話同事會覆返嚟 但到依家電話都未響過</blockquote>"},{"pid":"556ab819d65caebb165f2244019cadfafcc28550","tid":205994,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時打去開通d咩服務都要對下資料係咪本人啦。<br />\n叫佢呀媽告個女盜用身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁應該唔洗罰款。</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以話以為係cut合約？ 幾個鐘錢打俾佢佢有話有錄音 話同事會覆返嚟 依家電話都未響過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就要睇對話內容。如果冇好明確咁講係打黎續約，任你up，屌番佢轉頭都仲得。<br />\n<br />\n你依家試下話明明記得係打黎cut合約對資料，之後要求聽錄音先，聽清楚再睇下點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffdf6bd0d226fdd2a3d253dd1fb9da0cf15c8269","tid":205994,"uid":5429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時打去開通d咩服務都要對下資料係咪本人啦。<br />\n叫佢呀媽告個女盜用身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁應該唔洗罰款。</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以話以為係cut合約？ 幾個鐘錢打俾佢佢有話有錄音 話同事會覆返嚟 依家電話都未響過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就要睇對話內容。如果冇好明確咁講係打黎續約，任你up，屌番佢轉頭都仲得。<br />\n<br />\n你依家試下話明明記得係打黎cut合約對資料，之後要求聽錄音先，聽清楚再睇下點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我依家就係要求佢俾錄音 到依家已經三四個鐘 佢都冇俾任何錄音或者打俾我<br />\n其實係咪代表佢冇錄音？"},{"pid":"de4b99297abd254bf0955cc0be01396a440a8889","tid":205994,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時打去開通d咩服務都要對下資料係咪本人啦。<br />\n叫佢呀媽告個女盜用身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁應該唔洗罰款。</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以話以為係cut合約？ 幾個鐘錢打俾佢佢有話有錄音 話同事會覆返嚟 依家電話都未響過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就要睇對話內容。如果冇好明確咁講係打黎續約，任你up，屌番佢轉頭都仲得。<br />\n<br />\n你依家試下話明明記得係打黎cut合約對資料，之後要求聽錄音先，聽清楚再睇下點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我依家就係要求佢俾錄音 到依家已經三四個鐘 佢都冇俾任何錄音或者打俾我<br />\n其實係咪代表佢冇錄音？</blockquote><br />\n應該冇，正常錄前會聽到錄音講:以確保服務質素以下對話內容將會被錄音咁。<br />\n應該係"}]}